</label></span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Au cas où le chargement des produits est assuré  par le VENDEUR, les frais seront incorporés au prix de vente.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:12.0pt; ">Article  9 – L&rsquo;enregistrement </span></u></strong></p>
